353
00:29:37,120 --> 00:29:39,930
To je roztomilé.

354
00:29:39,930 --> 00:29:41,420
Mami, o čem to tu mluvíte?

355
00:29:41,420 --> 00:29:45,200
Už se to stalo, proč bych o tom nemohla mluvit?

356
00:29:45,200 --> 00:29:49,210
Jen o tom říkám Yun Duo.

357
00:30:00,280 --> 00:30:06,060
